OL,3,CFinancial pressures force closure of
OL,4,C11 PSNI inquiry offices
OL,6,FPublic inquiry offices are set to
OL,7,Fclose at 11 police stations across
OL,8,FNorthern Ireland.
OL,10,FThe move, that will see four police
OL,11,Fstations in Belfast affected, as well
OL,12,Fas stations across the region, has
OL,13,Fbeen blamed on financial and resource
OL,14,Fpressures.
OL,16,FThe stations affected are Lisburn
OL,17,FRoad, Strand Town, Tennent Street and
OL,18,FWoodbourne in Belfast, as well as
OL,19,FBangor, Banbridge, Magherafelt,
OL,20,FDungannon, Lisnaskea, Waterside and
OL,21,FNewtownabbey.
