OL,3,CFinancial pressures force closure of
OL,4,C11 PSNI inquiry offices
OL,6,FThe inquiry office closures are likely
OL,7,Fto take place within the three months,
OL,8,Fand are designed to make a significant
OL,9,Ffinancial saving as well as maximise
OL,10,Fthe availability of officers for
OL,11,Fcritical service provision within
OL,12,Fcommunities.
OL,14,FAssistant Chief Constable Bobby
OL,15,FSingleton said the decision was "not
OL,16,Ftaken lightly".
