OL,3,CFinancial pressures force closure of
OL,4,C11 PSNI inquiry offices
OL,6,F"Last month the Chief Constable
OL,7,Finformed the Northern Ireland Policing
OL,8,FBoard that as a consequence of the
OL,9,Fcurrent financial and resource
OL,10,Fpressures facing the Police Service,
OL,11,Fthe decision has been taken to reduce
OL,12,Fthe number of station inquiry offices
OL,13,Ffrom 28 to 17," he said.
OL,15,F"This decision follows an extensive
OL,16,Freview which included analysis of the
OL,17,Fvolume and type of demand in inquiry
OL,18,Foffices.
