OL,3,CFinancial pressures force closure of
OL,4,C11 PSNI inquiry offices
OL,6,FThis review concluded that against the
OL,7,Fbackdrop of wider resource challenges,
OL,8,Fthe current service is neither
OL,9,Fsustainable nor effective.
OL,11,F"This is not a decision we have taken
OL,12,Flightly and we are conscious there may
OL,13,Fbe an actual or perceived loss of
OL,14,Faccessibility, visibility and ability
OL,15,Fto respond to the needs of the
OL,16,Fcommunity.
