OL,3,CFinancial pressures force closure of
OL,4,C11 PSNI inquiry offices
OL,6,F"However, the PSNI is facing
OL,7,Funprecedented financial pressure and
OL,8,Fsavings are necessary to deliver a
OL,9,Fsustainable and effective
OL,10,Forganisation."
OL,12,FHe added: "It is important to
OL,13,Femphasise that these are not station
OL,14,Fclosures. Police officers and staff
OL,15,Fwill continue to serve the community
OL,16,Ffrom these locations."
OL,18,FThe Police Federation said the planned
OL,19,Fclosures come as "the inevitable
OL,20,Fconsequence of budget pressures".
