OL,3,CFinancial pressures force closure of
OL,4,C11 PSNI inquiry offices
OL,6,FPFNI Chair Liam Kelly, said: "I
OL,7,Funderstand that communities that are
OL,8,Faffected will view this decision with
OL,9,Fdismay and disappointment.
OL,11,F"That said, severe cuts in service
OL,12,Flevels are the outworking for an
OL,13,Forganisation that faces a deficit of
OL,14,F#130 million.
OL,16,F"Something has to give if core
OL,17,Fpolicing services are to be maintained
OL,18,Fwith the diminishing resources that
OL,19,Fare available.
